
### Create a simple Dockerfile

Based on laracast https://laracasts.com/series/the-docker-tutorial/episodes/2

Commands:
 - Build container
```
docker build --no-cache -t laravel-nginx .
```

- Run the container
```
docker run --rm -p 80:80 -v ~/vetster/laravel-docker.test/src:/var/www/html/public laravel-nginx
```

- Take container ID
```
docker ps
```

- Stop Container
```
docker stop 'container-id-from-docker-ps'
```
